<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Trello Insights – Professional Reports for Trello</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: #f8fafc;
            color: #0f172a;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

        header {
            background: #0079BF;
            padding: 20px 0;
            color: white;
        }
        header .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .logo span {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 25px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.85;
        }
        .nav a:hover { opacity: 1; }

        .hero {
            padding: 70px 0 50px;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f4fd 0%, #d4e8f5 100%);
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 44px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #0f172a;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .hero h1 span { color: #0079BF; }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #334155;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
        }
        .hero .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #0079BF;
            color: white;
            padding: 6px 18px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .hero .price-box {
            display: inline-block;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 121, 191, 0.15);
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .hero .price-box .price {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #0079BF;
        }
        .hero .price-box .price span {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        .hero .price-box .sub {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .cta-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #0079BF;
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 50px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .cta-btn:hover { background: #026AA7; }
        .cta-btn.green { background: #36B37E; }
        .cta-btn.green:hover { background: #2d9d6b; }

        .guarantee {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border: 2px solid #86efac;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto 0;
        }
        .guarantee strong { color: #16a34a; }

        .features {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background: white;
        }
        .features h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }
        .feature-card .icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .feature-card h3 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .feature-card p { color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; }

        .pricing {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background: #f1f5f9;
        }
        .pricing h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .pricing-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .pricing-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 35px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }
        .pricing-card.popular {
            border-color: #0079BF;
            position: relative;
        }
        .pricing-card.popular::before {
            content: "⭐ Most Popular";
            position: absolute;
            top: -12px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #0079BF;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .pricing-card .price {
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        .pricing-card .price span {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        .pricing-card ul {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .pricing-card ul li {
            padding: 6px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #334155;
        }
        .pricing-card ul li::before { content: "✅ "; }
        .pricing-card .cta-btn { font-size: 16px; padding: 12px 40px; }

        .testimonials {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background: white;
        }
        .testimonials h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .testimonial-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }
        .testimonial {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .testimonial .stars { color: #f59e0b; font-size: 18px; }
        .testimonial p { font-size: 14px; color: #334155; margin: 10px 0; }
        .testimonial .author { font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
        .testimonial .role { font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; }

        footer {
            background: #0f172a;
            color: #94a3b8;
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        footer a { color: #94a3b8; text-decoration: none; }
        footer a:hover { color: white; }
        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 30px; }
            .hero .price-box .price { font-size: 36px; }
            .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .testimonial-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .nav a { margin-left: 15px; font-size: 13px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            📊 Trello Insights
            <span>Built for Trello</span>
        </div>
        <div class="nav">
            <a href="#features">Features</a>
            <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
            <a href="#testimonials">Testimonials</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="badge">🔥 Now Available – One-Time Purchase</div>
        <h1>Professional Reports for <span>Trello</span></h1>
        <p>Generate stunning reports, track blocked cards, automate tasks, and get a live dashboard — all in one tool.</p>

        <div class="price-box">
            <div class="price">$39 <span>one-time</span></div>
            <div class="sub">Includes 1 year of updates • No subscription</div>
        </div>

        <br />
        <a href="#pricing" class="cta-btn">🚀 Get Trello Insights Now</a>

        <div class="guarantee">
            💵 <strong>30-Day Money-Back Guarantee</strong> — If you're not satisfied, we'll refund your purchase. No questions asked.
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="features" id="features">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>What's Inside?</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon">📊</div>
                <h3>Professional Reports</h3>
                <p>One-click HTML reports with stats, charts, and card details. Print to PDF for clients.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon">📈</div>
                <h3>7-Day Trend Chart</h3>
                <p>See how overdue, stale, and completed cards change over time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon">🚧</div>
                <h3>Blocked Card Detection</h3>
                <p>Automatically find cards stuck in "Blocked" or "Waiting" lists.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon">⚡</div>
                <h3>Automation Actions</h3>
                <p>Move stale cards, assign overdue, add blocked labels, and comment on stale — all with one click.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon">🖥️</div>
                <h3>Live Dashboard</h3>
                <p>Key metrics at a glance: total cards, overdue, stale, completed, and bottleneck alerts.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon">🎨</div>
                <h3>Report Customization</h3>
                <p>Choose exactly which sections appear in your report — tailor it for clients or internal teams.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="pricing" id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Choose Your Plan</h2>
        <div class="pricing-grid">
            <div class="pricing-card popular">
                <h3>Pro (One-Time)</h3>
                <div class="price">$39 <span>one-time</span></div>
                <ul>
                    <li>Full tool (reports + dashboard + automation)</li>
                    <li>1 year of free updates</li>
                    <li>Email support</li>
                    <li>30-day money-back guarantee</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="[YOUR_GUMROAD_LINK]" class="cta-btn">Buy Now – $39</a>
            </div>

            <div class="pricing-card">
                <h3>Lifetime Updates</h3>
                <div class="price">$59 <span>one-time</span></div>
                <ul>
                    <li>Full tool (reports + dashboard + automation)</li>
                    <li><strong>Lifetime</strong> free updates</li>
                    <li>Priority email support</li>
                    <li>30-day money-back guarantee</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="[YOUR_GUMROAD_LINK]" class="cta-btn green">Buy Now – $59</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align:center; margin-top: 20px; color: #64748b; font-size: 14px;">
            🔒 Secure payment via Stripe • Instant download • License key included
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="testimonials" id="testimonials">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>What Users Are Saying</h2>
        <div class="testimonial-grid">
            <div class="testimonial">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"This tool saved me hours of manual reporting. I can generate a beautiful client report in 10 seconds."</p>
                <div class="author">— Sarah K.</div>
                <div class="role">Project Manager, Agency</div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"The automation actions are a game-changer. I can now move stale cards and assign overdue cards with one click."</p>
                <div class="author">— Marcus R.</div>
                <div class="role">Freelance Consultant</div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p>"I love the dashboard — I can see my entire project health at a glance without opening Trello."</p>
                <div class="author">— Elena M.</div>
                <div class="role">Team Lead, Startup</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="#">Home</a>
            <a href="#features">Features</a>
            <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
            <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a href="#">Terms</a>
        </div>
        <p>
            © 2026 Trello Insights. Built for Trello users everywhere.
            <br />
            <span style="font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.7;">Trello is a registered trademark of Atlassian. Not affiliated with Trello.</span>
        </p>
    </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
